{
  "stem": "8916.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know the immediate feeling as a boy I recall I was, well, I don't have to go to school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then that only lasted for 10 seconds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there was everything that was going to go on in school was passing me by.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because my father's work and his life is a middle-class level of-- of income, as soon as the war broke out, his savings and his [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] security disappeared immediately.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So really as soon as-- as the war broke out we had to start looking around to see how we could help each other and help the family to survive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not a possibility.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That option was not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Germans occupied Poland in 1939, the Russians occupied the eastern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When that happened, Narewka became under the control of the Soviets, so there was no way to-- to move from one side to the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just occasionally somebody smuggled across the border and ended up-- came from Narewka.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we used to have good contact because those people who worked in the factory where my father was the tool and die maker also came from Narewka, where they had non-Jews who had connections and family in Narewka.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they worked in Krakow and had family in Narewka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was the Krakow Glass Factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lots, lots of times.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I used to hang around his place of work and watch him do his machining.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I picked up a little bit of that from just watching him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
